Text: hello crap! I downloaded the first season from someone else and it was junk quality, I thought this torrent was the same season...17 seasons??? I thought this show was cancelled years ago. But son discovered it and loves it, so thanks a bunch! The files are more than twice the size of the other torrent, so I am hoping quality is much better!

is there going to be a continuation?

this looks like a "to be continued..." to me, the way it ends and all.

The show's original creator Haim Saban has re-acquired Power Rangers from Disney, so this is no longer the final season. Saban is working on Season 18 to air in early 2011 on Nickelodeon.

But with the story and cast changing every year, I doubt there will be a continuation. It's still the best of the Disney seasons IMO though. :)
